{
  "stem": "4693.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I found out that when the ghetto was burning, they had, like Luna Park here-- a big wheel.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So the Poles were going-- it was Easter-- were going on this wheel to look how the Jews are burning.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was told by a friend of mine, who was younger, was to school with me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was-- officially he was Polish, he was half Jewish.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he was in the high command of the-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] underground army, was called [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he told me how the Poles were denouncing the Jews, how they were shooting them, even during the uprising.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The Jews were with them together in the uprising against Germans, and they were shot in the back.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "This was the confirmed to me by others later.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Look, to me, it was a colossal shock because I was very assimilated.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I considered myself a Pole, until the certain time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And it was-- I never want to go to Poland.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I got into Vienna.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were a few days in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we left already in sealed cars through the Russian territory, into Germany, into the American zone of Germany.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When we arrived in Germany, Munich was destroyed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I went to Steinberg am See, and it looked very nice.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a beautiful place.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I got, from Munich, positioned at palace home there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this where we moved in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In fact, this was not far from the-- all around were plenty of Jewish displaced person camps.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I went to Feldafing, where there was number of people from the same region where I came from.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[DRINKS] And then I started working as a civilian employee for UNRRA.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "UNRRA was the United Nations Refugee and Relief Agency.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was taking care of displaced persons.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
